Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:49.69,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}记忆如花瓣般衰败消散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:01:01.37,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}触碰的瞬间 破碎散落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.33,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}带我走吧!
